description:
In Viviter's multiplayer mode, you can play "Chickempic" with up to 8 players, and we're adding the "Just barely: impossible" mini-game!
The mission this time is to steal data from the computer.
However, the security is flawless, so the only way is to sneak in from the top floor!
That's where you come in!
Quickly infiltrate from the top floor and lower the rope to the floor!
You can do it! Note that this switch will automatically disappear (just kidding).
name: Additional mini-game "Just barely:impossible"
